data.description: This spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is great for entertaining with its dining area, family room, living room & open kitchen. The 2-car garage is also air conditioned for additional comfort. The master bedroom is a separate from the other rooms to provide additional privacy and has a large master bathroom with an oversized tub and separate shower stall. Plenty of closet space throughout. Roof was replaced in 2020 and the A/C was replaced in 2023.  Located in a quiet and peaceful neighborhood not far from schools. Conveniently located 19 miles from Disney parks, I-Drive entertainment district, 20 miles from Universal Park, and 10 miles from I-4.
